{"tid":84454,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有台灣仔發現香港丸久小山園係盜用人個名搵食?","createTime":"2017-01-17T14:07:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T21:14:00.000Z","uid":42582,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ffb3a3eeb8aa10c169da92d2978563adf2a0c00","tid":84454,"uid":42582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:07:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MACHACAKE/posts/1377430698995226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMACHACAKE%2Fposts%2F1377430698995226&d=bkMff%2BmN1HGnJVfal0EyEQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=99dcf48b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MACHACAKE/posts/1377430698995226</a><br />\n<br />\n前幾日分享的香港丸久小山園消息<br />\n有版友到日本本店詢問過後得知<br />\n並非丸久小山園本店出資<br />\n<br />\n雖然商品都是出自京都本店的貨源<br />\n不過也就是進了很多丸久小山園的東西<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去左丸久小山園個日本官網都唔見有海外店<br />\n相反中村藤吉個日本官網就搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd883f090041e1e189247b82b16868d9a3d7fb20","tid":84454,"uid":54582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6da2526edc12c34206946c097a69a1351f1974","tid":84454,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:16:07.000Z","msg":"過一排都執架啦"},{"pid":"017dc4cee607fac841c2de2d7148a5436ad45135","tid":84454,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a42eea65198a54a496a4d462ba4f7a439f01e73","tid":84454,"uid":42582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:19:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過一排都執架啦</blockquote><br />\n咁同(疑似)盜用兩樣野黎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid