c=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTVuR8ZyKoRan4aFj2wLzQQdeaP46cr41KcDCm4CMQSmp?filename=tC3wJhw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtC3wJhw.jpg&h=da22fa3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你劍心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c522bc0705d0f4f329defb719e096762bbe94f","tid":84454,"uid":25727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:00:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C2xne9xWEAAal80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC2xne9xWEAAal80.jpg&h=00d6d82d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n笑咗 出番嚟繼續呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829e19135b8dcf9bc0d237cc0b53325663fb0059","tid":84454,"uid":38206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:24:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講到咁撚寸，好期待日本出公開聲明收佢皮</blockquote><br />\n個台灣人講野真係好討厭"},{"pid":"e4ad2e95f3e41d31324c383dcd0ee74ae4d92d9e","tid":84454,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:58:40.000Z","msg":"《OFF TOPIC - 疑似日本元組級綠茶店於香港被中資集團欺詐事件》<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，幾個禮拜前從於日本從事綠茶工作的友人H口中得知呢件事，但由於當時事件未曝光，成件事又唔關CCTVB事，我就冇喺度講，不過事件已有幾個page報咗出嚟，我都唔怕加多一腳。<br />\n<br />\n前一排有一間疑似香港企業approach日本嘅一間元組級綠茶店（下稱店A），希望引入店A嘅綠茶產品，而店A一向亦有為香港某餅店提供綠茶原料出品線茶味嘅甜品，心諗香港人都算信得過，亦冇同餅店嘅合作構成任何影響，就簽署賣貨合約，同意提供店A嘅貨品到呢間香港企業作賣。<br />\n<br />\n過咗一排，店A嘅日本總部聽到有人問佢哋喺香港開咗分店，佢哋都澄清話佢哋只係賣貨，唔係開店。直至有日客人send咗本地報導，佢哋先知俾人利用咗。<br />\n<br />\n本來店A打算出禁制令禁止該店繼續營業，但有人卻暗示會大事宣揚店A嘅店喺香港開幾個禮拜就做唔住，幾百年字號會因此而受損，所以店A唯有同呢間香港企業談判。<br />\n<br />\n朋友H因與店A嘅人相熟，代爲查探下發現原來呢間所謂香港企業疑似係中資公司。<br />\n<br />\n朋友H認為，唯一方法就係廣傳呢段消息，等大家都知道呢間香港店其實唔係店A嘅正式分店，只係幫店A入貨，仲要擅自用店A名義出品自家產品嘅公司，咁店A先放心割席。<br />\n<br />\n我唯痿雖然個page得200幾人，但相信網友嘅良心同力量，有與趣又睇唔過眼嘅朋友可以關心吓呢件事。<br />\n<br />\n#利申我都係聽返嚟<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ilovewaiwaiibrushshoes/posts/363772520653808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Filovewaiwaiibrushshoes%2Fposts%2F363772520653808&d=bkMff%2BmN1HGnJVfal0EyEQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=c420c015\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ilovewaiwaiibrushshoes/posts/363772520653808</a>"},{"pid":"7d14e908c9f43db5fb5fe3b72762bd7f17b26e70","tid":84454,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T17:19:27.000Z","msg":"中資企業要俾錢日本賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a232ff18e035052f9de93c514d533308b6f6bc49","tid":84454,"uid":68712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T17:34:04.000Z","msg":"依單野一出 一大班食家同港女已經表曬態話唔幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea49e954bf97ddc6a3eb60383176dbf1a18a5255","tid":84454,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T18:07:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTVuR8ZyKoRan4aFj2wLzQQdeaP46cr41KcDCm4CMQSmp?filename=tC3wJhw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtC3wJhw.jpg&h=da22fa3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012116b099dafde476fc8b15893bbb2c7b9fe88f","tid":84454,"uid":5818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T20:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7c3cc14900549adccd0650e97cb810e5914076","tid":84454,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T02:32:23.000Z","msg":"又要跟廖仔<br />\n又要緊backup狗<br />\n冇人理呢單柒出國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n說好的聯合聲明呢？"},{"pid":"677fd8a312ed588f4c62dc0358698f120f8b7041","tid":84454,"uid":65578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:31:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f43de54c824a3c62c83191b64643c6576e20a1f5","tid":84454,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:35:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講到咁撚寸，好期待日本出公開聲明收佢皮</blockquote><br />\n個台灣人講野真係好討厭</blockquote><br />\n抵俾人串啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03085b6254db5dfc325e67872f8de3fef91438d","tid":84454,"uid":38665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:01:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTVuR8ZyKoRan4aFj2wLzQQdeaP46cr41KcDCm4CMQSmp?filename=tC3wJhw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtC3wJhw.jpg&h=da22fa3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本達人都讚，點會係假呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6644ab900a225035dfde18d804e91794c500dfa2","tid":84454,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:12:55.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple_sub/a.php?i=20